---

Admin Dashboard Purpose

The Admin Dashboard is designed to be the main control center for the entire platform.

The admin will use this dashboard to manage:

Users
Subjects
Courses
Lessons
Videos
Access Codes
Purchases
Enrollments
Security
Platform overview

The dashboard is not a simple page.

It is a complete management system inside the frontend.

---

Why We Created a Separate Dashboard Folder

Instead of placing all admin pages randomly inside:

src/pages/

We created a dedicated admin dashboard structure:

src/dashboard/admin/

This keeps the project organized and scalable.

Reason:

The admin dashboard will become large over time.

It will contain many pages, forms, tables, filters, modals, API files, and types.

Keeping everything inside one organized folder prevents frontend code from becoming messy.

---

Final Admin Dashboard Structure

