Shared Folder

Path:

src/dashboard/admin/shared/

Purpose:

This folder contains reusable components used across multiple admin modules.

Shared components prevent repeated code.

Instead of creating a new table, search bar, badge, or modal inside every module, we create reusable components once and use them everywhere.

Shared Components

Path:

src/dashboard/admin/shared/components/

Files:

DashboardCard.tsx
DataTable.tsx
SearchBar.tsx
StatusBadge.tsx
ConfirmModal.tsx
EmptyState.tsx

DashboardCard.tsx

Used to display statistics in the Overview page.

Example:

Total Courses
Total Students
Total Purchases

DataTable.tsx

A reusable table component.

Used in:

Users
Subjects
Courses
Lessons
Purchases
Enrollments
Access Codes
Security

SearchBar.tsx

A reusable search input.

Used to search inside admin pages.

StatusBadge.tsx

Used to display status visually.

Examples:

Active
Inactive
Published
Unpublished
Completed
Pending
Used
